I was in tears by the end of the song! it was not only mind blowing but also soul touching! I wish I could comment on each and every part of this version of the song separately, but I have no words for that.... the "Allah" in the end was mesmerizing....

No matter what country/religion/ culture you belong to... music composed and songs sung from the heart... reaches the heart of the listeners... and that's how it connects us... 

Grand solute to all the musicians and singers involved in this video.
